OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain cloudy during the evening and
OL,7,Fthrough the night with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain, turning heavy and perhaps
OL,9,Fthundery from late evening. Gentle
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloud and occasionally heavy,
OL,13,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing.
OL,14,FThen sunny spells and scattered
OL,15,Fshowers, occasionally heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
