OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry,
OL,6,Fbright start in east Monday before
OL,7,Fcloud and outbreaks of rain soon
OL,8,Fspread east. Mostly cloudy Tuesday and
OL,9,FWednesday with rain or showers, heavy
OL,10,Fand thundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
